      "description": "OpenFOAM RANS (SST k-omega) velocity fields compared against FDA GCBP PIV measurements at 2500, 3500, and 5000 RPM across three flow rates. All 5 operating points completed with nominal solver convergence (residuals below 1e-5). No solver exceptions or NaN values were reported in any run.",
      "outcome": "Passed",
