      "rationale": "SST k-omega selected based on prior literature demonstrating superior performance in rotating machinery flows with adverse pressure gradients. Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis model applicability documented for shear stress ranges 1–600 Pa encountered in this COU. Model form uncertainty estimated at ±18% for RH predictions based on sensitivity to turbulence model constants."
    },
    {
