      "rationale": "One-at-a-time sensitivity analysis performed for fluid viscosity (±5%), hemolysis model exponent alpha (±10%), and rotational speed (±50 RPM). RH sensitivity to viscosity: 3.2% per 5% viscosity change. Sensitivity to alpha: 8.7% per 10% change. Rotational speed sensitivity: 4.1% per 50 RPM. Combined input uncertainty estimated at ±11% for RH."
    },
